<https://pod.rubendedecker.be/scholar/projects/deployEMDS/catalogs/dataset_catalog#Catalog> dcat:dataset <https://pod.rubendedecker.be/scholar/projects/deployEMDS/datasets/sample_dataset1>.
<https://pod.rubendedecker.be/scholar/projects/deployEMDS/datasets/sample_dataset1> a dcat:Dataset;
